00:13:25,742 --> 00:13:27,283
and getting back into action really quickly.

315
00:13:27,303 --> 00:13:28,284
It's all about that.

316
00:13:28,664 --> 00:13:30,466
But Dead Cells is really combat-oriented.

317
00:13:30,906 --> 00:13:34,830
Platforming, it's just a mean to move and to avoid enemies

318
00:13:34,890 --> 00:13:35,951
and to position yourself.

319
00:13:36,031 --> 00:13:39,034
It's not an hardcore platformer game.

320
00:13:39,835 --> 00:13:41,397
When we asked this question, it was really

321
00:13:41,497 --> 00:13:43,059
useful to many points.

322
00:13:43,659 --> 00:13:44,701
Is it meant to be a challenge?

323
00:13:44,761 --> 00:13:47,584
I mean, is the player supposed to die doing this?

324
00:13:48,044 --> 00:13:50,427
And if the answer is no, yes, we just

