345
00:14:34,035 --> 00:14:36,337
And that's lots of things like that we actually

346
00:14:36,397 --> 00:14:38,798
do which are behind the curtain that actually make sure

347
00:14:38,818 --> 00:14:41,360
that the player succeeds in doing what he wants to do.

348
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:44,201
First thing, this one is a very common thing.

