00:14:54,103 --> 00:14:57,584
we actually give you two or three frames to jump anyway.

354
00:14:58,044 --> 00:14:59,724
Because we understand that you wanted to jump

355
00:14:59,944 --> 00:15:03,025
on the last split second, and you clearly missed.

356
00:15:03,405 --> 00:15:05,646
But yeah, it's not meant to be a challenge.

357
00:15:05,666 --> 00:15:07,326
So OK, you can jump.

