00:19:42,336 --> 00:19:45,720
And it really works like that.

484
00:19:46,580 --> 00:19:49,343
Actually, for the one year on alpha early access,

485
00:19:49,403 --> 00:19:52,085
I think we maybe had two people noticing this thing.

486
00:19:52,506 --> 00:19:56,269
It's a kind of hidden trick that actually makes life easier.

487
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:59,592
Because missing the enemy by attacking the wrong direction,

488
00:20:00,053 --> 00:20:00,874
it's just not fun.

489
00:20:01,034 --> 00:20:03,416
We don't want that to happen, especially in a combat game.

490
00:20:04,237 --> 00:20:06,278
And the same goes, for example, for ranged weapons.

491
00:20:06,478 --> 00:20:09,539
We have a slight auto-aim, which is, of course, more obvious.

492
00:20:10,039 --> 00:20:11,900
But this one has a few tricks.

493
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:15,161
For example, if you have a very fast weapon, a fast bow,

494
00:20:16,162 --> 00:20:19,723
we'll have a higher priority on small enemies.

495
00:20:20,364 --> 00:20:22,304
those who are low on HP or whatever,

496
00:20:22,364 --> 00:20:24,345
or maybe a big enemy with low on HP,

497
00:20:24,665 --> 00:20:25,385
or this kind of stuff.

498
00:20:25,445 --> 00:20:27,486
Maybe it's really close from you, about to eat you.

499
00:20:27,886 --> 00:20:30,086
So we have a priority system on targets.

500
00:20:30,547 --> 00:20:32,147
It's really different from using, for example,

501
00:20:32,167 --> 00:20:35,508
a very slow, powerful longbow, like a sniper or something.

502
00:20:35,948 --> 00:20:38,709
In this case, we just want you to eat the big targets.

503
00:20:38,769 --> 00:20:40,850
You don't want to eat some crappy trash mob.

504
00:20:41,170 --> 00:20:43,230
You just want to focus on eating the big target.

505
00:20:43,571 --> 00:20:44,631
So it's really all about that.

506
00:20:45,191 --> 00:20:47,832
making sure that we actually understand what the player wants to do,

507
00:20:48,252 --> 00:20:51,213
and making sure that it feels like he was actually in power,

508
00:20:51,233 --> 00:20:53,974
he was in control, and he managed to do everything.

