00:21:12,135 --> 00:21:13,715
He shoots at us.

518
00:21:13,856 --> 00:21:14,656
So we cancel.

519
00:21:15,076 --> 00:21:17,897
And we move to this guy, kicking to the wall.

520
00:21:18,537 --> 00:21:21,518
And this guy above is throwing a bomb on us.

521
00:21:21,558 --> 00:21:22,938
So we get behind him.

522
00:21:23,478 --> 00:21:23,978
We kick him.

523
00:21:24,598 --> 00:21:26,219
And he falls on his friend.

524
00:21:27,239 --> 00:21:28,860
When someone falls on the ground in this game,

525
00:21:29,100 --> 00:21:30,321
