00:24:48,346 --> 00:24:50,849
And especially if it's not the core of the game.

603
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:53,212
This game, Dead Cells, is not a platforming game.

604
00:24:53,552 --> 00:24:54,273
It's a combat game.

605
00:24:54,293 --> 00:24:55,394
It's a progression game.

606
00:24:55,814 --> 00:24:57,116
As I said, stuff like that.

