00:24:57,797 --> 00:24:59,298
But it's not a hardcore platformer.

608
00:24:59,318 --> 00:25:02,682
But still, because platforming is part of the game.

609
00:25:03,042 --> 00:25:05,483
But we don't want that to get in the way of the player.

610
00:25:06,184 --> 00:25:09,585
We just actually take extra care, actually much more care

611
00:25:09,645 --> 00:25:12,426
about controls, for example, than anything else.

612
00:25:12,626 --> 00:25:15,968
Because we don't want that to be an issue in any way, and

613
00:25:16,148 --> 00:25:17,228
also because of the permadeath.

