00:25:59,733 --> 00:26:00,973
It's really not fun.

628
00:26:01,473 --> 00:26:03,313
And lots of things have evolved.

629
00:26:03,693 --> 00:26:06,154
And it's really all about getting the feelings

630
00:26:06,174 --> 00:26:08,875
that you had from this game and transforming back

631
00:26:08,915 --> 00:26:11,535
into your game, not copying things,

632
00:26:11,615 --> 00:26:13,896
because it's really not interesting, I think.

